txt.en: You have turned in a stack of trophies for a modest reward suitable for a collector such as yourself.
Wanted: Huge ears from the beasts surrounding Aughaire. Deliver the items to Raith at Aughaire in the south-western reaches of Angmar.
'These will ornament our items well. Thank you.'
'The ears taken from the beasts around us serve us well as ornamentation.'
Council of the North Task: Huge Ears
The Hillmen at Aughaire have requested a collection of huge ears to be delivered to Raith.
Deliver the huge ears to Raith at Aughaire in Angmar
You have accepted a task to collect and deliver huge ears from beasts surrounding Aughaire to Raith, a Hillman within the settlement.
Wanted: Huge ears from the beasts surrounding Aughaire.
